    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paint by Pixel 是一款既有趣又放松的游戏，非常适合发挥创意。想象一下，一个舒适的艺术体验，在这里你可以一像素一像素地为美丽的像素艺术上色。无论你是喜欢用画笔模式来进行细致的处理，还是用填充模式快速实现你的构想，你都可以轻松地个性化你的创作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244050/extras/c8c290b2525b8978cf738fc07eee9c5b.poster.avif?t=1729573730\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244050/extras/c8c290b2525b8978cf738fc07eee9c5b.webm?t=1729573730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244050/extras/c8c290b2525b8978cf738fc07eee9c5b.mp4?t=1729573730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索独特的关卡，确保每一个像素都恰到好处。选择你最喜欢的颜色，使每一件艺术作品真正属于你自己。控制简单，适合初学者，所以你会喜欢每一刻制作这些像素杰作的时光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244050/extras/fd5d7b9b6a079581f96c8f8883d45393.poster.avif?t=1729573730\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244050/extras/fd5d7b9b6a079581f96c8f8883d45393.webm?t=1729573730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244050/extras/fd5d7b9b6a079581f96c8f8883d45393.mp4?t=1729573730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paint by Pixel 是当你想要做一些可爱、舒适又有趣的事情时的完美游戏。它非常适合你的创意时刻，而且非常容易上手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试试看，看看你能在创作像素艺术中找到多少乐趣吧！</p>",
